print welcome or game intro message with fancy 3D title

assign a random number to a unique variable as the answer to guess

while their guess is not equal to the answer,
	prompt user to guess the number and assign it to variable "guess"
	if the guess is greater than answer
		print "it's lower"
	elseif the guess is less than answer
		print "it's higher"
	keep count of attempted guesses
		
print "you got the answer!" and show how many attempts it took to guess the answer

print "game over"
